1. *Snimak* je snimljen pre nekoliko sati. (The recording was made a few hours ago.)
2. Ona je zabeležila *snimak* događaja. (She recorded the event.)
3. On je napravio nekoliko *snimaka* sa putovanja. (He made several recordings from the trip.)
4. Oni su imali *snimak* nesreće. (They had a recording of the accident.)
5. Da li imate *snimak* njene govore? (Do you have a recording of her speech?)
6. Oni su uzeli *snimak* sa njegove kamere. (They took a recording from his camera.)